nodes.text: Phanuel was a musical artist who became a part of the Mon Calamarian diaspora scene around five years before the Battle of Yavin. While the artist was still relatively new in the scene, the Mandalorian artist and demolitions expert Sabine Wren listen to some of Phanuel's work and then wrote in her journal that it was amongst her favorite music that she had recently listened to.
Phanuel was first mentioned in Sabine My Rebel Sketchbook, a reference book written by Daniel Wallace and published in 2015.
